runs.text: IMPORTANT - The Cognito Platform Has Launched

accessibilityData.label: IMPORTANT - The Cognito Platform Has Launched by Cognito 244,804 views 2 years ago 5 minutes, 22 seconds

runs.text:
- Today we officially launched the Cognito platform. The platform's been designed to make your learning and revision as quick and easy as possible. All your progress is automatically tracked so you can immediately see what you need to learn, and all the content is delivered in a straight-forward, no-fluff way. We really hope this helps you out, and if you could do us a favour by letting everyone know it exists, we'd be really grateful.

Thank you so much for your support, and if you have any feedback please let us know. We read every comment.

Amadeus & Tom

channelTaglineRenderer.content: Hi - we make video lessons for GCSE science and maths. The lessons give a concise run through of everything you'll need to know for your exams.

title.simpleText: About

channelMetadataRenderer.title: Cognito
channelMetadataRenderer.description:
Hi - we make video lessons for GCSE science and maths. The lessons give a concise run through of everything you'll need to know for your exams.

Each video has been designed specifically for the 9-1 GCSE courses, and although they most closely mirror the AQA spec, everything you need to know for the main exam boards will be covered.

We also have a website where you can work through the lesson videos and answer a series of practice questions to check you know all the required learning points. All your progress is automatically tracked, and you can sign up at www.cognitoedu.org

Best wishes,

Amadeus & Tom
